CONTENT: * **Bipartite Graph:** A graph where vertices define two disjoint sets ($V_A, V_B$) with edges strictly connecting $V_A$ to $V_B$ [(§1.5.1)](/monograph/rules/ontology/1.5/#1.5.1).
