FILE: 01-rules/03-architecture/3.1.md L56
CONTENT: 7.  **Principle of Unique Causality:** Information cannot be cloned: specific paths must be unique to serve as valid candidates for interaction [(§2.3.3)](/monograph/rules/axioms/2.3/#2.3.3).
