FILE: 01-rules/03-architecture/3.2.md L73
CONTENT: 2. **The Sparsity and Connectivity Filters (Lemma [§3.2.4], Lemma [§3.2.5]):** The argument excludes disconnected states and redundant acyclic graphs, restricting the candidate space to minimally connected directed tree topologies.
