FILE: 01-rules/03-architecture/3.2.md L74
CONTENT: 3. **The Homogeneity Optimization (Lemma [§3.2.6], Lemma [§3.2.7], Lemma [§3.2.8]):** The argument enforces orbit transitivity, site maximality, and degree regularity, isolating the regular Bethe fragment as the sole structure that maximizes symmetric homogeneity.
