CONTENT: The **dimensionful VEV scaling lemma** [(§8.6.4)](/monograph/players/braids/8.6/#8.6.4) anchors the dimensionless graph to real-world units. Prior lemmas established that the VEV scales as $v \propto \sqrt{\rho_3^* N_\xi}$, where $N_\xi$ is the number of 3-cycles contained strictly within a local correlation volume $V_\xi$.
